aws_ec2_transit_gateway_route_table.description: Manages an EC2 Transit Gateway Route Table

tags.description: Key-value tags for the EC2 Transit Gateway Route Table.

default_association_route_table.description: Boolean whether this is the default association route table for the EC2 Transit Gateway.
